Name: RedSun RTS
About the game: Redsun RTS is a prime example of the genre classic RTS, unjustly forgotten today. In this game you directly and as speaks for itself the name of the genre, real-time control armies, build a base, plan attacks and to strengthen the defense on the battlefield. At your disposal different types of units - each with their own tasks, strengths and weaknesses.
